is or has become inaccurate, incomplete, misleading, misrepresenting, and incorrect. You may request in writing to access to your personal data to change and update your information. However, we have the right to use our discretion in allowing any corrections requested and/or require further documentary evidence of the new data to avoid any fraud or inaccuracy of data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Third Party Link</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">There may be Third Party Websites provided on the Website. This is for your conveniences in accessing to other information and we hold no responsibility for any damage or losses occur by relying on the Third Party Websites. Further this privacy policy only applies to our Website and shall not extend to any third party links. Please ensure that you read their own privacy policies.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Disclosure</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to third parties your personal information. However, we may also release your information when we believe it is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours and others’ rights, property or safety. Unless permitted or required to do by law, we will never disclose any information which is classified as “sensitive personal data” without your explicit consent.</p>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1438-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-24 09:16:11', '2016-10-24 09:16:11', '', 1438, 'http://ethiscrowd:8888/2016/10/24/1438-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
