idth="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1223" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_06.png" alt="business_icon_06" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1221" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_01.png" alt="business_icon_01" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tg">\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1240" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/business_icon_09.png" alt="business_icon_09" width="175" height="50" /></td>\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1241" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/business_icon_04.png" alt="business_icon_04" width="175" height="50" /></td>\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1242" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/business_icon_02.png" alt="business_icon_02" width="175" height="50" /></td>\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1243" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/business_icon_03.png" alt="business_icon_03" width="175" height="50" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[krown_section background="white"]\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Experiences</h5>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Why investors love Ethis</h3>\r\n[rev_slider alias="testimonial"][/krown_section]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="extreme">Islamic Crowdfunding has never been that easy.     </span> [krown_button size="large" style="color" label="Learn More" url="#"][/krown_column]</p>', 'Home #1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '835-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-17 17:59:19', '2017-01-17 09:59:19', '', 835, 'http://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/835-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2184, 7, '2017-01-17 18:12:58', '2017-01-17 10:12:58', '<h4>Introduction</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The company takes your privacy very seriously. You are encouraged to read this privacy policy carefully as it contains important information about what to expect when we collect personal information about you and how we use your personal information. By accessing to our Website or services, you agree to obey the Website Privacy Policy herein.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Contact</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you have any questions in regards to our website privacy policy, please do not hesitate to contact us with any queries or comments by sending us an email to legal@ethisaficf.ethisdev.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Amendment</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We constantly review our Website Privacy Policy to ensure that it is always updated. Hence we reserve the rights to amend and/or revise and/or modify these Website privacy Policy from time to time without explaining or give any reason or highlighting to you what are the changes made. The amendments will be uploaded to the Website immediately and it is your duty to regularly review information published on the Website page. Your continue use indicates the acceptance of the amended Website Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Information collected from visitors on our website</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will acquire personal data about you when you visit us. When you visit us, we may monitor the use of this Site through the use of cookies and similar tracking devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Cookies</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We may use cookies on our Website which enables us to collect standard Internet log information and visitor behavior information. You can set your browser not to accept cookies. However, in a few cases some of our Site features may not function if you remove cookies from your browser</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Protecting information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We are committed to maintain the security of personal information. There will be in place an appropriate security procedures and technical and organization measure to safeguard your personal information.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Personal Information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You may be required to provide us information about yourself by using the online forms provided on the Website. This includes, without limitation, information you provide when you register to use the Website, enter into a transaction via the Website, participate in discussion boards or other social media functions on the Website and/or when you report a problem with the Website or our services.</p>\r\nThe information you give us may include:\r\n\r\n(a) your name;\r\n(b) your date of birth;\r\n(c) your current and (where necessary) previous postal address;\r\n(d) your telephone number and email address;\r\n(e) Information relating to your employment, income, financial and personal circumstances;\r\n(f) Information relating to ay businesses or companies which you may have an interest; and\r\n(g) Where applicable, specific documents which verify your identity and any other personal information.\r\n<h4>Use of Your Information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We may use your Information obtained by us as set out in this Privacy</p>\r\nPolicy for the purpose of :\r\n\r\n(a) Delivering our products and Services to you\r\n(b) Improving our products and Services to you\r\n(c) Marketing and Advertising our products and Services to you\r\n(d) to verify your identity in order to prevent and detect money laundering and fraud\r\n(f) to carry out credit reference checks\r\n(g) to carry out market research\r\n(h) to notify you about any changes to our services\r\n(i) to keep you informed about fees and charges\r\n<h4>Updating and correcting your information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You have the right to request access to your personal data and to correct your personal if it is or has become inaccurate, incomplete, misleading, misrepresenting, and incorrect. You may request in writing to access to your personal data to change and update your information. However, we have the right to use our discretion in allowing any corrections requested and/or require further documentary evidence of the new data to avoid any fraud or inaccuracy of data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Third Party Link</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">There may be Third Party Websites provided on the Website. This is for your conveniences in accessing to other information and we hold no responsibility for any damage or losses occur by relying on the Third Party Websites. Further this privacy policy only applies to our Website and shall not extend to any third party links. Please ensure that you read their own privacy policies.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Disclosure</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to third parties your personal information. However, we may also release your information when we believe it is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours and others’ rights, property or safety. Unless permitted or required to do by law, we will never disclose any information which is classified as “sensitive personal data” without your explicit consent.</p>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1438-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-17 18:12:58', '2017-01-17 10:12:58', '', 1438, 'http://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/1438-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
